description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated individual to join the HealthRoster Team within the Human Resources Department at Liverpool Heart and Chest Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The principal role of the post will be to be the first line support for the areas in the Trust that are utilizing the Trusts chosen Electronic Rostering systems This includes Healthroster, Bankstaff, Allocate ME/Employee Online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous knowledge and use of Allocates rostering system and delivering training is required together with excellent IT &amp; communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should be able to demonstrate willingness and a capability to learn, possess excellent communication and interpersonal skills and the ability to motivate and inspire others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the job description and person specification for further details on the role.&lt;/p&gt;
